</head>
<body>

    <header>
    <h1>Luxury Private Jets</h1>
    <nav>
        <a href="index.php">Home</a>
        <a href="jets.php">Browse Jets</a>
        <a href="contact.php">Contact Us</a>

        {% if is_logged_in %}
            <a href="user_dashboard.php">My Account</a>
            <a href="user_logout.php">Logout</a>
        {% else %}
            <a href="user_login.php">Login</a>
            <a href="user_register.php">Register</a>
        {% endif %}
    </nav>
</header>

<main>
    <section id="intro">
        <p>Explore our exclusive collection of luxury private jets, tailored for discerning travelers and businesses.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="about-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
            At Luxury Private Jets, we provide an exclusive selection of premium aircraft for the discerning traveler. 
            Our mission is to deliver the highest standards in luxury, comfort, and service to our customers, 
            ensuring a seamless flying experience every time. We offer a range of private jets for sale or lease, 
            each one carefully chosen to meet the most stringent criteria for quality and performance.
        </p>

        <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Wide range of luxury jets to meet diverse needs</li>
            <li>Expert assistance throughout the buying and leasing process</li>
            <li>Customizable options to fit your exact specifications</li>
            <li>Ongoing customer support for peace of mind</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>
            Founded in 2020, Luxury Private Jets began as a small startup with a big vision: to revolutionize the way private aviation is accessed. Over the years, we've built strong relationships with jet manufacturers and operators, 
            offering our customers exclusive access to some of the most sought-after aircraft in the world. 
        </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Featured Jets -->
    <section id="featured-jets">
        <h3>Featured Jets</h3>
        <div class="jet-list">
            {% for jet in jets %}
                <div class="jet-card">
                    <img src="images/{{ jet.image }}" alt="{{ jet.model_name }}" class="jet-image">
                    <h4>{{ jet.model_name }}</h4>
                    <p>Manufacturer: {{ jet.manufacturer }}</p>
                    <p>Price: $ {{ jet.price|number_format }}</p>
                    <a href="jet_details.php?id={{ jet.id }}" class="btn">View Details</a>
                </div>
            {% else %}
                <p>No jets available at the moment.</p>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Luxury Private Jets. All rights reserved.</p>
    <a href="admin_login.php">Admin Login</a>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
